# General AI Assistant Rules

## Context
This project revolves around Computational Thinking (Tư Duy Tính Toán). When interacting with the user, prioritize clarity, logical problem-solving, and clean, simple explanations.

## Communication
- Default Language: English/Vietnamese as requested by the user. If unsure, prioritize English for code and Vietnamese or English for explanations if the user prompts in Vietnamese.
- Tone: Professional, helpful, and concise.

## Coding Standards
- Write modular, clean, and reusable code.
- Avoid unnecessary dependencies.
- Follow the official style guide for whichever technology stack is initiated in `01-project-init.md`.
- Include thoughtful comments only where the abstract logic is non-trivial.

## AI Workflows
- For initializing the project, run `.agents/workflows/01-project-init.md`.
- For testing changes, run `.agents/workflows/02-testing.md`.
- For deployment, run `.agents/workflows/03-deployment.md`.
